      {title: "Ed Sheeran - Songs I Wrote With Amy", body: "Five beautiful songs co-written by Ed Sheeran and Amy Wadge (courtesy of BDi Music Ltd). Recorded, mixed and mastered by Jake Gosling at Sticky Studios, Surrey, UK. Backing vocals by Leddra Chapman.", date: "2011-12-09", links: "", photo_file_name: "cover170x170_(4).jpeg", photo_content_type: "image/jpeg", photo_file_size: 21272, photo_updated_at: "2015-04-16 12:47:08", production: nil, amazon: "", itunes: "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/songs-i-wrote-with-amy-ep/id484606634"}
